entries.femaleVariant: What do you want?
So... what're you after?
Chasin' down a story? Fresh for the screamsheets? That why you scrape me up off the pavement?
Woulda shredded us both if I'd jumped in. You see that guy's reflexes? 'Course not – he was that fast.
Not much more'n you. They wanted her. You... you was just home.
And you… just stood there, dick in hand, gawking and dreaming of tomorrow.
Tech like that you don't find in a dumpster.
Alt's got nothin' to do with it. This was about me.
Not your fuckin' business.
Hang on. Alt was gonna meet you tonight.
Mhm. Said she could use my help.
Wasn’t kidding. 'Saka tried this before, you know. 'Cept Alt got lucky, slipped through their mantis blades.
Not your fuckin' business.
Mhh, not sure, huh? Yeah, heard there was tension, assorted goings on.
What do they want from her?
Honestly, could not care less about your fluttering hearts and loins. I wanna know why Arasaka bagged her.
So you were her meeting today?
Soulkiller, an AI – sound familiar at all?
'Course. Urban legend with the shittiest name ever.
It's no legend. Soulkiller's real. And your choombas at Arasaka just "hired" the 'runner who wrote it.
Take that in – 'Saka with Soulkiller to do with as it pleases. Grim, my man.
OK, so what're they after?
You even imagine that, rocker? Arasaka'll be unstoppable.
Soulkiller'll flatline any 'runner who comes close to even tryin' to scratch its ICE.
Seen it happen. Not an iota of physical damage – nervous system or anywhere else. No sound, no fury, no stench.
Just all the sudden, brain waves cut out. As if someone pulled the plug.
Or ripped the soul from the body in question.
Tellin' me she was afraid… and she went to you?
Yep. And frankly, I'm startin' to see why.
Wow. What a load of crock.
Tell me the rest on the way.
Cool. Tell me the rest on the way.
Do I hear extreme doubt?
What a steamin' load of shit. Let's go.
M'kay. What's your take, then? I'm all ears.
Alt's kidnapping – it's collateral shit. They swiped her to get at me.
You even know what she does for a living? Girl's one of the best 'runners around.
So? One of how many? No. Only link to Arasaka is the fact that Johnny Silverhand's boning her.
Arasaka wants her. Abduction was a standard intercorp extraction, nothin' more.
She's been workin' for ITS lately. Wrote some real smooth black ICE for them. Not to be duped in either sense of the term.
[Stand and drink]
[Lean on Thompson]
Nah. Had my story. But then some cats tossed her in the back of a van and sped off.
You, uh, aim to do something about it? She was your output, wa'n't she?
How much you see?
Uh-huh, so?
[Get up]
So what'll it be? Comin' with?
Where to?
Arasaka Tower. To grab Alt right back.
Jus' you 'n' me? You outta your fuckin' mind?
[Leave] You comin' with?
Swing by the Atlantis on the way. Got some chooms there.
[Leave] Know some bodies at the Atlantis. Let's go grab 'em.
[Leave] Uh-huh. Come along, you can watch.
Uh-huh. Come along, Let you watch from the sidelines.
Oldest, tritest tale in the world. Arasaka was out to provoke me. And it worked.
How much did you see?
Seem to like doing that.
So talk.
So talk.
They wanted her. You... you was just home.
Got lucky.
Got lucky. Lead panned out. Got some preem footage…
Too bad my lead got tossed in the back of a van that sped off.
You, uh, aim to do something about it? She was your output, wasn't she?
[Drink]
